From 1fbe0f2d937a14959ad9cd1286244ef6fb10a792 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Z User <z@container>
Date: Tue, 21 Apr 2026 17:51:55 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] feat: DataSphere Agents v2 - Full upgrade
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Renamed datasphere_agent → datasphere_agents (consistent naming)
- Enhanced all agent system prompts (support, finance, data, sales, webbuilder, image, custom)
- Improved RAG context with smart chunking for data/finance/support agents
- Added webbuilder and image agent types to execution agents
- Agent-type-based temperature and max_tokens configuration
- Fixed image button - opens dialog for user to describe image
- Fixed mic button - shows voice input coming soon toast
- Fixed social login buttons - show toast notifications
- Fixed forgot password button - shows toast notification
- Enhanced ChatView with auto-resizing textarea and Ctrl+Enter to send
- Improved MobileNav with Web Builder tab and haptic feedback
- Improved DashboardView with 2-column mobile stats, gradient cards, shortcuts
- Improved AgentsView with category tabs, popular badge, hover animations
- Improved LoginView with responsive social buttons
- Added MarketplaceView with search, filters, rating, install, publish
- Created security.ts with rate limiting, input sanitization, validation
- Added rate limiting to login (5/min), register (3/min), chat-stream (20/min)
- Added input validation and sanitization to auth and chat routes
- Improved Sidebar with gradient line, notification bell, tooltips
- Improved SettingsView with connection status dots, test connection, avatar
- Added premium CSS utilities (card-hover, status-dot, shimmer-loading, focus-ring)
- New backend: auth.py, database.py, dependencies.py, models.py, schemas.py
- New backend services: ai_service.py, rag_service.py
- New frontend: layout.tsx, globals.css, store/useStore.ts, lib/api.ts
- Added Next.js config, Tailwind config, PostCSS config, TypeScript config
- Removed old datasphere_agent directory (singular naming)
