From a8a6b0aeb2540fa755e4b775048c7edd636366d2 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Z User <z@container>
Date: Tue, 21 Apr 2026 18:38:45 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] feat: DataSphere Agents v3 - Next.js 16 full-stack app

Complete rewrite as a unified Next.js 16 full-stack application:

- Migrated from separate Python/FastAPI backend to Next.js API Routes
- 9 specialized AI agents with professional system prompts
- Multi-provider AI (OpenAI, Anthropic, Groq, Qwen, OpenRouter + z-ai-sdk fallback)
- Streaming chat (SSE) with Markdown rendering and code highlighting
- JWT authentication with bcrypt password hashing
- SQLite database via better-sqlite3 / Drizzle ORM
- Marketplace with search, install, rate, publish
- Image generation via AI
- Web Builder agent for site generation
- Document management and RAG capabilities
- Responsive UI with shadcn/ui components
- Mobile-optimized with bottom navigation
- API key management per provider
- Rate limiting and input validation (security.ts)
- Zustand state management
- Professional dashboard with stats and activity
- Dark mode support via theme provider

Removed:
- Old Python FastAPI backend (replaced by API Routes)
- Old separate frontend (now integrated in src/)
- Docker/nginx configs (simplified deployment)
- Old datasphere_agent/ directory
